<!DOCTYPE html>
<html>
    <head>
        <title>Customer SMS Transaction</title>
        <meta charset='UTF-8'>
        <meta name='viewport' content='width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0'>
        <style type='text/css'>
            body{
                font-family:Arial;
                font-size: 11pt;
            }
            table{
                text-align: center;
                border-right:1px solid black;
                border-bottom:1px solid black;

                border-collapse:collapse;
                font-family:Arial;
                font-size: 10pt;
                width: 60%;
            }
            td, th{
                border-left:1px solid black;
                border-top:1px solid black;
            }
            .colHeading{
                background-color: #D6D8EC;
            }
            span{
                font-weight:bold;
            }
        </style>
    </head>
    <body>Dear {{REALNAME}},
        <p>Yesterday's sms consume details :</p>
        <br/>
        <table border='1'>
            <tr><th colspan="4" class="colHeading">Sms Transactions For {{REPORT_DATE}}</th></tr>
            <tr>
                <th class="colHeading">Sr No</th>
                <th class="colHeading">Mobile No</th>
                <th class="colHeading">Message</th>
                <th class="colHeading">Time</th>
            </tr>
            {{DATA_ROWS}}
        </table>
        <br/>
        <br>
        <p>Please feel free to contact us on <strong>022-2513-7471</strong> or email us at <strong>support@elixiatech.com</strong> in case you have any queries regarding using the system. </p>
        <br/>
        Warm Regards, <br/>
        Support Team,<br/>
        Elixia Speed<br/>
        Elixia Tech Solutions Ltd.<br/><br/>
        <img style="width: 240px;" src = "http://speed.elixiatech.com/images/elixia_logo_75.png" alt = "Elixia Speed logo" />
        <br/>
    </body>
</html>
